去嗰到開公司，拎永久居留證。<br />\n<br />\n好耐之前香港得 500 萬人口，依家漲到 700 萬。香港嘅出生率唔到。多出嚟嘅大家心中有數。<br />\n<br />\n每日 150， 專才計劃，你睇個 d 嚟香港讀碩士個堆，有幾多係香港人。25 年都未有，香港人口暴漲。"},{"pid":"29875f221149901f7daf689712816d5dee7cc957","tid":1664264,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1374b3a9a650637522b75ea297fd898d98e6f31","tid":1664264,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27f96ee632f9cebdcc3982732e7d56e4bd87094b","tid":1664264,"uid":24641,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:50:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇唔到除左賭場 澳門有咩吸引之處"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T04:38:37.000Z","msg":"佢想搞金融交易所喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:18:39.000Z","msg":"薑蓉雞翼所？ 澳門最出名叫雞，應該有得搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f66262ce422a7fb2d6bab620c1f3e29874bd64","tid":1664264,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:22:42.000Z","msg":"敵人擁護的...rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9d52395f048b55b0a6c5199a8b62f6eed69cf4","tid":1664264,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"76162346f846cf10c94bf15933ee2496338faf84","tid":1664264,"uid":155137,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"27f96ee632f9cebdcc3982732e7d56e4bd87094b","tid":1664264,"uid":24641,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:50:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇唔到除左賭場 澳門有咩吸引之處"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:52:21.000Z","msg":"佢哋有葡藉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T06:23:22.000Z","msg":"以前d人就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class